Reasoning: The paper deals with the secrecy capacity of a wiretap erasure broadcast channel, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of cache memories and the optimization of cache assignment suggest a possible connection to networking (cs.NI) and systems and control (cs.SI). The paper also mentions joint cache-channel coding, which is a technique used in multimedia communication (cs.MM).
